\par
``TextBlob'' (Ison, 2026, p. 2) Python library used to do NLP tasks.
\par
``--4]. Topic modeling techniques, particularly Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA), have been widely used to uncover hidden structure in large text corpora [3], while transformer-based approaches such as BERTopic (Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers-based topic modeling) have demonstrated improved semantic coherence [15].'' (Ison, 2026, p. 3)
\par
