\begin{itemize}

\item \textbf{Baseline finding:} Seasonal variation exists in UAS sighting data
\item \textbf{Method precedent:} Chi-Square Goodness of Fit is acceptable for this dataset
\item \textbf{Replication opportunity:} I can verify/extend these findings with 4x more data
\item \textbf{Gap identified:} Regional analysis needed; causal factors untested

\end{itemize}

\subsubsection{What My Research Can Add}

