\item \textbf{Temporal extension:} Verify if seasonal patterns hold across 12 years
\item \textbf{Regional decomposition:} Extract location data to test regional variations
\item \textbf{Multi-variable analysis:} Examine relationships between extracted fields
\item \textbf{Trend analysis:} Assess whether patterns change over time (e.g., pre/post Remote ID)

\end{enumerate}

