This article ~is a recent example of drone flights interfering with manned flight operations and resulted in a midair collision between the drone and the aircraft. ~The wing of the aircraft sustained damage and was grounded and resulted in 1 of the 2 Super Scooper aircraft assigned to mission being grounded until repair could be completed.
